com.abmash.api.browser

Class History

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.abmash.api.browser.History

  • public class History
extends java.lang.Object
    Interaction with browser history, used by calling Browser.history().

    This class is used to move back and forward in the browser history.

    Author:
    Alper Ortac
